</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-84_ pf-text-1"><strong>Prepare first aid kits</strong> - Ensure that homes, cars, and child care settings are equipped with first aid kits that include supplies necessary for treating nosebleeds.



















